subtitle: casey had had this sort of experience
before
but never quite like this it wasn't a
panic attack per se

a moment where everything he understood

up until more recently casey never

course he had free will
he felt it in every moment what could
possibly be the issue or question

consequently he had become more

casey began to question the obviousness
of his own
free will specifically

these things directly affected and led

thereafter
in an unbroken linear sequence of cause

thus
every new spur thereafter everything

the advent of the internet the invention

no biological or physiological necessity

nothing other than his own willful

to himself

casey obviously concluded it was being

in truth he concluded he was no

casey ruminated in his head about this

on the following monday on his way to

know

casey did nothing after a few extra long

after another brief pause casey replied
